00:02:31,472 --> 00:02:33,968
=Episode 21=

16
00:02:39,759 --> 00:02:40,320
Mr. Lin.

17
00:02:41,080 --> 00:02:43,360
Lei Yuzheng had quite a fall this time.

18
00:02:43,839 --> 00:02:46,520
It'll take a while for him
to make a comeback.

19
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:49,080
I didn't expect that.

20
00:02:49,679 --> 00:02:50,559
I…

21
00:02:50,919 --> 00:02:52,279
What didn't you expect?

22
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:56,240
Nothing.

23
00:02:57,880 --> 00:03:01,320
Mr. Lin, it's good that
Lei Yuzheng is gone now.

24
00:03:01,639 --> 00:03:03,320
Why do you still seem
to worry a lot?

25
00:03:03,600 --> 00:03:05,559
You can take this chance
to get promoted, right?

26
00:03:05,880 --> 00:03:06,839
Promoted?

27
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:10,759
I, Lin Xiangyuan, will never
take advantage of other people.

28
00:03:11,600 --> 00:03:13,839
I was gonna fight with
Lei Yuzheng face to face.

29
00:03:14,440 --> 00:03:15,520
If I win then,

30
00:03:15,759 --> 00:03:17,279
it means that
I am really  more capable than him.

31
00:03:18,440 --> 00:03:20,800
But the result means everything.

32
00:03:21,119 --> 00:03:22,919
As long as you become the president of Yutian,

33
00:03:23,199 --> 00:03:25,080
no one cares about
what means you took.

34
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:28,119
They will all look up to you.

35
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:38,800
Xieli,

36
00:03:39,759 --> 00:03:42,839
what do you think
Lei Yuzheng is doing right now?

37
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:44,199
What else can he do?

38
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:47,839
He must be crying out loud at the court.

39
00:03:48,880 --> 00:03:51,279
Now, the old is in hospital,

40
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:52,919
and the young is in jail.

41
00:03:53,320 --> 00:03:56,000
Now it's time for you, Mr. Lin,
to take charge.

42
00:04:01,639 --> 00:04:03,880
Mr. Jiang, directors are waiting for you
to join the meeting.

43
00:04:06,199 --> 00:04:10,440
Look at this,
these reporters are going way too far.

44
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:13,360
They used such title as
"Yutian's stock market scandal" and

45
00:04:13,679 --> 00:04:15,679
"Construction of Entertainment Center
project might be called off".

46
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:17,679
They are talking nonsense.

47
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:22,039
Mr. Jiang,
that's what reporters usually do.

48
00:04:22,279 --> 00:04:23,360
As long as they can make
a big news out of something,

49
00:04:23,479 --> 00:04:25,000
they would exaggerate everything.

50
00:04:25,119 --> 00:04:26,440
Speaking of that,

51
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:28,039
not only those reporters,

52
00:04:29,039 --> 00:04:30,839
but also our employees are

53
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:31,880
talking about rumors right now.

54
00:04:32,919 --> 00:04:33,839
What do you mean?

55
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:36,720
They are all saying that

56
00:04:37,160 --> 00:04:39,119
it will take a while for Lei Yuzheng
to make a comeback.

57
00:04:39,279 --> 00:04:40,960
And if no one takes the lead right now,

58
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:43,000
the Entertainment Center project
will be affected.

59
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:44,240
Mr. Jiang,

60
00:04:45,279 --> 00:04:47,359
everyone is waiting for you
to take the lead.

61
00:04:50,279 --> 00:04:51,760
But I don't know much about

62
00:04:52,640 --> 00:04:54,760
the Entertainment City project.

63
00:04:55,239 --> 00:04:56,559
If I take over right now,

64
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:58,399
isn't it too hasty?

65
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:00,079
I might trap myself

66
00:05:00,559 --> 00:05:03,440
later on.

67
00:05:05,880 --> 00:05:06,880
By the way, Mr. Jiang,

68
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:09,079
is Fanlv feeling better?

69
00:05:09,440 --> 00:05:10,559
How's her appetite?

70
00:05:10,839 --> 00:05:12,679
I'm planning to go back to my hometown,

71
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:14,279
and bring some delicacies
for her to improve her health.

72
00:05:15,559 --> 00:05:16,679
Fanlv is fine.

73
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:19,279
Xiangyuan, you are very thoughtful.

74
00:05:22,079 --> 00:05:24,920
Ah, regarding the
Entertainment Center project,

75
00:05:25,239 --> 00:05:27,880
you know it the best
besides Lei Yuzheng.

76
00:05:29,839 --> 00:05:31,920
Come and join the meeting with me.

77
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,799
Lin, have a seat.

78
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:58,480
Regarding what happened to
Yutian recently,

79
00:05:59,200 --> 00:06:00,959
I don't have to recap it.

80
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:04,000
Why don't all of you

81
00:06:04,279 --> 00:06:05,679
contribute your ideas?

82
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:08,279
Such a big company

83
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:10,720
needs a leader.

84
00:06:10,839 --> 00:06:13,720
Jiang, you should think of a way.

85
00:06:16,519 --> 00:06:17,600
Yuzheng is in trouble,

86
00:06:18,559 --> 00:06:20,320
and brother Ting is in the hospital.

87
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:22,559
Everyone must be very anxious.

88
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:24,760
But it's still important

89
00:06:25,079 --> 00:06:28,079
to maintain the order
within the company.

90
00:06:28,880 --> 00:06:30,480
Why don't we vote by raising hands

91
00:06:31,119 --> 00:06:33,920
to elect a temporary president
to take charge for now?

92
00:06:34,839 --> 00:06:35,679
How does that sound?

93
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:37,600
As far as I'm concerned,
we can skip that step.

94
00:06:37,799 --> 00:06:39,440
The one who can take charge
is you, Mr. Jiang.

95
00:06:39,640 --> 00:06:40,720
You should take this position.

96
00:06:41,279 --> 00:06:42,000
Me?

97
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:45,119
No, no, no. How could it be me?

98
00:06:46,279 --> 00:06:47,559
Don't be modest.

99
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:50,920
The Entertainment Center project
belonged to Xinsheng in the first place.

100
00:06:51,079 --> 00:06:53,640
Although Yutian is in charge of
the development,

101
00:06:53,799 --> 00:06:55,079
you also have the responsibility.

102
00:06:55,640 --> 00:06:57,239
Mr. Jiang, don't be so modest.

103
00:06:57,640 --> 00:06:58,920
Mr. Jiang, you should take it.

104
00:06:59,040 --> 00:07:00,160
Mr. Jiang, I will vote for you.

105
00:07:00,239 --> 00:07:00,679
I agree.

106
00:07:00,839 --> 00:07:01,679
Yes, I agree.

107
00:07:02,839 --> 00:07:05,040
All right. Since everyone has
such high expectation in me,

108
00:07:06,799 --> 00:07:09,160
and we should take the overall interests
of the company into account.

109
00:07:09,799 --> 00:07:13,399
I will just take this position for now,

110
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:15,920
and hope everyone could understand.

111
00:07:16,119 --> 00:07:18,000
Of course.

112
00:07:18,839 --> 00:07:23,720
But a leader cannot fight by oneself.

113
00:07:24,239 --> 00:07:26,480
It's not enough to do it all

114
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:28,119
by myself.

115
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:33,119
Lin has been my assistant
for so many years.

116
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:36,160
We've built great rapport
with each other.

117
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:37,920
Everyone here has witnessed

118
00:07:38,119 --> 00:07:40,320
his ability.

119
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:43,079
So I suggest that I will supervise

120
00:07:43,279 --> 00:07:45,880
the Entertainment Center project,
and Lin will be in charge.

121
00:07:52,640 --> 00:07:55,959
I know that Lin is my future son-in-law,

122
00:07:56,239 --> 00:07:58,799
and I should have left him out of this,
so that people won't gossip about it.

123
00:07:59,119 --> 00:08:02,679
But to the benefit of Yutian
and the Entertainment Center project,

124
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:06,000
I think we can entrust Lin
with this task.

125
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:09,640
Lin, the investment that
you were working on

126
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:11,160
is still possible, right?

127
00:08:11,519 --> 00:08:13,760
I'll keep working on it.
I think it is possible for us to get it.

128
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:18,920
If Lin can collect money
for the Entertainment Center project,

129
00:08:19,119 --> 00:08:20,959
he will be the hero of Yutian.

130
00:08:21,239 --> 00:08:22,959
We can't even thank him enough.

131
00:08:28,640 --> 00:08:29,640
Everyone,

132
00:08:30,760 --> 00:08:32,279
at the very beginning,
Xinsheng cooperated with Yutian

133
00:08:32,519 --> 00:08:35,160
on the Entertainment Center project
by offering it as a gift.

134
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:37,119
Since the board has decided

135
00:08:37,519 --> 00:08:38,959
that I will take charge of this project,

136
00:08:39,119 --> 00:08:40,760
I know how much responsibility I have.

137
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:42,920
I won't let anyone down.

138
00:08:56,020 --> 00:08:58,239
(Police)

139
00:09:04,839 --> 00:09:06,599
(Jiangkan Detention Center)

140
00:09:08,039 --> 00:09:08,799
Get off the car.

141
00:09:13,199 --> 00:09:14,579
(Jiangkan Detention Center)

142
00:09:21,679 --> 00:09:23,760
According to Article 180

143
00:09:23,760 --> 00:09:25,400
of the Criminal Law
of the People’s Republic of China,

144
00:09:25,719 --> 00:09:29,280
the defendant Lei Yuzheng,
the prior president of Yutian,

145
00:09:29,520 --> 00:09:31,200
is sentenced for 8 month detention
(Jiangkan Detention Center)

146
00:09:31,359 --> 00:09:32,880
due to the charge of
disclosing confidential information,

147
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:34,760
and immediate execution is required.

148
00:09:36,860 --> 00:09:39,499
(Silence)

149
00:09:43,599 --> 00:09:44,880
Time is a one way road.

150
00:09:46,119 --> 00:09:47,559
You can only move forward
without going back.

151
00:09:48,559 --> 00:09:50,239
There's no pure luck in this world.

152
00:09:50,799 --> 00:09:53,960
Everyone needs to pay the price
for their mistakes.

153
00:09:57,520 --> 00:09:58,400
Go inside.

154
00:10:46,359 --> 00:10:47,280
My name is Liu Siyang.

155
00:10:49,280 --> 00:10:50,479
It must be the first time for you.

156
00:10:51,039 --> 00:10:52,000
I can tell that
you're not used to here yet.

157
00:10:58,359 --> 00:10:59,679
It will be better in a few days.

158
00:11:19,599 --> 00:11:20,559
Here you are.

159
00:11:22,039 --> 00:11:24,400
Xiaosu, it was on TV.

160
00:11:24,719 --> 00:11:26,440
Did Lei Yuzheng actually go to jail?

161
00:11:30,840 --> 00:11:32,239
I couldn't do anything about it.

162
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:34,200
There was no evidence and

163
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:36,320
nothing was beneficial towards him.

164
00:11:37,159 --> 00:11:38,880
He also didn't want to explain about it,

165
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:42,239
and took all the responsibilities
by himself.

166
00:11:42,640 --> 00:11:43,679
So,

167
00:11:44,919 --> 00:11:47,159
I couldn't do anything
but watching him get accused.

168
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:50,799
It's all my fault.

169
00:11:51,280 --> 00:11:52,760
I couldn't do anything.

170
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:55,479
I couldn't help him.

171
00:11:56,239 --> 00:11:57,599
What happened to Lei Yuzheng this time

172
00:11:57,640 --> 00:11:59,520
is really a big issue.

173
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:01,159
Since when...

174
00:12:06,239 --> 00:12:07,119
Siqi,

175
00:12:11,559 --> 00:12:12,719
Let's break up.

176
00:12:16,679 --> 00:12:17,679
What did you say?

177
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:19,559
Mr. Lei went to jail,

178
00:12:21,760 --> 00:12:23,080
and the chairman is in a coma.

179
00:12:25,239 --> 00:12:26,880
It's all because of me.

180
00:12:28,479 --> 00:12:29,719
Since the past cannot be changed,

181
00:12:30,520 --> 00:12:31,799
I cannot just sit here and

182
00:12:31,919 --> 00:12:33,880
have date with you.

183
00:12:35,719 --> 00:12:38,119
He Qunfei, what is wrong with you?

184
00:12:39,159 --> 00:12:40,559
Don't regret if you say this.

185
00:12:40,760 --> 00:12:42,159
There's nothing to regret.

186
00:12:43,520 --> 00:12:45,080
Things are already this bad.

187
00:12:46,559 --> 00:12:48,479
I deserve whatever it costs.

188
00:12:49,840 --> 00:12:50,960
He Qunfei, don't be so impulsive.

189
00:12:51,039 --> 00:12:52,159
You can leave this behind.

190
00:12:53,599 --> 00:12:54,640
He Qunfei,

191
00:12:55,640 --> 00:12:56,799
you wanna break up, right?

192
00:12:58,400 --> 00:13:00,440
From now on, let's go our own ways.

193
00:13:00,599 --> 00:13:01,799
Don't you dare regret it.

194
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:02,320
Siqi.

195
00:13:02,479 --> 00:13:04,000
He Qunfei, get out of here now.

196
00:13:04,200 --> 00:13:05,359
Now.

197
00:13:05,719 --> 00:13:07,359
Siqi, calm down.

198
00:13:09,039 --> 00:13:09,960
Xiaosu.

199
00:13:10,760 --> 00:13:12,440
I really appreciate your help
this whole time.

200
00:13:13,520 --> 00:13:14,599
See you.

201
00:13:27,840 --> 00:13:29,840
What are you two doing?

202
00:14:02,880 --> 00:14:03,919
You can't fall asleep, right?

203
00:14:05,080 --> 00:14:06,880
There're only two of us

204
00:14:07,760 --> 00:14:09,039
in this 9-square meter room.

205
00:14:09,479 --> 00:14:11,159
If you keep silent like this,

206
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:13,039
it won't be long till

207
00:14:13,559 --> 00:14:14,840
we both got crazy.

208
00:14:28,719 --> 00:14:29,919
You seem to be

209
00:14:30,799 --> 00:14:32,320
someone who has power,

210
00:14:33,400 --> 00:14:35,080
and can't bear with living in jail.

211
00:14:35,919 --> 00:14:36,960
No wonder.

212
00:14:37,880 --> 00:14:39,080
Rich people,

213
00:14:50,919 --> 00:14:52,080
who's like you,

214
00:14:53,640 --> 00:14:55,880
always seem proud when nothing happens.

215
00:14:56,599 --> 00:14:58,239
As long as they get troubled,

216
00:14:58,520 --> 00:15:01,559
they would look hopeless.

217
00:15:02,159 --> 00:15:04,159
I look down on people like you.

218
00:15:05,760 --> 00:15:06,880
What did you say?

219
00:15:07,760 --> 00:15:09,239
Nothing.

220
00:15:09,479 --> 00:15:11,200
I don't have respect
for people like you.

221
00:15:11,320 --> 00:15:12,440
Why?

222
00:15:15,760 --> 00:15:17,000
Too weak.

223
00:15:19,520 --> 00:15:20,559
You hit me?

224
00:15:22,080 --> 00:15:23,799
Hit me! Come, hit me!

225
00:15:25,479 --> 00:15:26,359
Hit me!

226
00:15:31,239 --> 00:15:31,799
Hit me!

227
00:15:32,559 --> 00:15:33,119
Stop it!

228
00:15:34,400 --> 00:15:35,159
Do it!

229
00:15:35,719 --> 00:15:36,440
What are you doing?

230
00:15:36,599 --> 00:15:37,599
What are you doing?

231
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:39,840
Stand aside.

232
00:15:41,799 --> 00:15:42,880
Who started first?

233
00:15:48,440 --> 00:15:49,119
Xiangyuan,

234
00:15:49,760 --> 00:15:51,159
was what Fanlv said true?

235
00:15:52,239 --> 00:15:55,159
Did He Qunfei really fight you?

236
00:15:55,919 --> 00:15:56,640
Yes.

237
00:15:57,159 --> 00:15:58,200
So, you do have something to do

238
00:15:58,640 --> 00:16:01,719
with Lei Yuzheng's trouble?

239
00:16:02,760 --> 00:16:04,919
Mr. Jiang, I've been serving you
for such a long time.

240
00:16:04,919 --> 00:16:06,400
How could you not trust me?

241
00:16:07,119 --> 00:16:08,239
How could I possibly do such

242
00:16:08,239 --> 00:16:09,640
disgraceful thing?

243
00:16:10,919 --> 00:16:11,559
Yes.

244
00:16:12,039 --> 00:16:14,000
He Qunfei fought me
because of Lei Yuzheng.

245
00:16:14,400 --> 00:16:16,119
But it was because
he cares about Lei Yuzheng so much

246
00:16:16,559 --> 00:16:17,919
that he lost his mind.

247
00:16:18,640 --> 00:16:20,840
He's been thinking of me
as Lei Yuzheng's enemy

248
00:16:21,840 --> 00:16:23,080
and always suspecting me.

249
00:16:24,880 --> 00:16:25,960
But I can understand that,

250
00:16:26,359 --> 00:16:27,880
because I was sent by Xinsheng anyway,

251
00:16:28,719 --> 00:16:30,000
and I don't have a direct relationship
with Lei Yuzheng.

252
00:16:30,159 --> 00:16:31,280
What do you mean by that?

253
00:16:32,000 --> 00:16:34,559
It was my idea to send you to Yutian

254
00:16:34,679 --> 00:16:36,200
for the Entertainment Center project.

255
00:16:37,359 --> 00:16:40,640
If He Qunfei is opinionative towards you

256
00:16:40,840 --> 00:16:42,039
just because of this,

257
00:16:42,159 --> 00:16:43,880
he's really shortsighted.

258
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:45,559
You don't have to care about him.

259
00:16:46,000 --> 00:16:46,719
Sure.

260
00:16:47,280 --> 00:16:49,119
I will keep it in mind.

261
00:16:49,960 --> 00:16:52,599
Dad, do you think it's that simple?

262
00:16:53,440 --> 00:16:54,400
Fanlv,

263
00:16:55,599 --> 00:16:56,799
do you think I can actually do

264
00:16:56,880 --> 00:16:58,440
anything that hurts Lei Yuzheng?

265
00:16:59,359 --> 00:17:00,320
Do I seem like a cunning person

266
00:17:00,760 --> 00:17:02,119
to you?

267
00:17:04,200 --> 00:17:05,960
I've never been fussy with you.

268
00:17:08,000 --> 00:17:09,080
You loved Lei Yuzheng,

