00:34:06,520 --> 00:34:08,000
and I'm just a prisoner.

551
00:34:09,239 --> 00:34:11,359
Do you want to be friends
with a prisoner?

552
00:34:12,479 --> 00:34:13,599
Lei Yuzheng,

553
00:34:14,839 --> 00:34:16,800
what kind of person do you think I am?

554
00:34:18,280 --> 00:34:20,239
Am I friends with you because of

555
00:34:21,239 --> 00:34:23,439
your fame or social status?

556
00:34:24,239 --> 00:34:25,079
Mr. Lei,

557
00:34:25,599 --> 00:34:28,119
Xiaosu has been really
worried about you.

558
00:34:28,959 --> 00:34:30,199
You didn't know it but

559
00:34:30,920 --> 00:34:32,800
she has been running around

560
00:34:33,239 --> 00:34:34,680
for you these days,

561
00:34:35,599 --> 00:34:37,000
and she's pined away.

562
00:34:38,120 --> 00:34:39,239
Du Xiaosu,

563
00:34:41,080 --> 00:34:42,840
stop being mawkish.

564
00:34:44,239 --> 00:34:46,000
Didn't you want to see me as a loser?

565
00:34:47,280 --> 00:34:49,159
Watching a person who used to be proud

566
00:34:49,360 --> 00:34:50,919
to fall to the bottom

567
00:34:51,280 --> 00:34:52,679
like me

568
00:34:53,520 --> 00:34:54,840
can satisfy your curiosity

569
00:34:54,840 --> 00:34:56,280
and compassion, right?

570
00:34:56,719 --> 00:34:58,719
I know what you are thinking.

571
00:34:59,239 --> 00:35:01,040
The once extremely arrogant Lei Yuzheng

572
00:35:02,159 --> 00:35:03,520
is no different than other people

573
00:35:03,560 --> 00:35:05,360
when he has lost everything.

574
00:35:05,760 --> 00:35:09,040
Maybe even worse than other people,

575
00:35:09,239 --> 00:35:10,479
isn't it?

576
00:35:12,360 --> 00:35:13,120
If it can make you feel better

577
00:35:13,120 --> 00:35:15,360
to see me like this,

578
00:35:16,639 --> 00:35:17,760
then say it.

579
00:35:18,479 --> 00:35:19,600
I'm listening.

580
00:35:20,360 --> 00:35:21,280
Du Xiaosu,

581
00:35:22,479 --> 00:35:23,520
save it.

582
00:35:24,120 --> 00:35:25,239
No matter it's your compassion

583
00:35:26,719 --> 00:35:27,560
or curiosity,

584
00:35:27,719 --> 00:35:29,439
you should be satisfied now.

585
00:35:30,639 --> 00:35:31,280
From now on, please

586
00:35:31,280 --> 00:35:33,080
