587
00:35:35,840 --> 00:35:37,000
and don't think about me again,

588
00:35:37,320 --> 00:35:38,679
or come here to visit me.

589
00:35:39,560 --> 00:35:40,959
Not to mention caring about me.

590
00:35:41,719 --> 00:35:42,639
Please leave.

591
00:35:50,760 --> 00:35:51,600
Lei Yuzheng,

592
00:35:53,879 --> 00:35:54,560
I...

593
00:35:59,800 --> 00:36:00,760
we will wait for you.

594
00:36:04,159 --> 00:36:07,399
Qunfei, you two can have a chat.

595
00:36:07,600 --> 00:36:08,639
I will be outside.

596
00:36:25,760 --> 00:36:26,719
Mr. Lei,

597
00:36:27,760 --> 00:36:29,719
I think you have some misunderstanding
about Xiaosu.

598
00:36:30,239 --> 00:36:32,000
It's been hard for her.

599
00:36:36,800 --> 00:36:38,399
I know that it's been hard for her.

600
00:36:41,040 --> 00:36:42,600
Just because I know it,

601
00:36:43,280 --> 00:36:45,000
I have to push her away.

602
00:36:45,959 --> 00:36:46,840
Don't you think that it's too selfish

603
00:36:46,919 --> 00:36:48,080
